A workflow from downloading an ERA5/GFS pres-level data file to GRIST-readable atmosphere initial file.

(1) go to download for getting ERA5/GFS data; for GFS, go to their webpage.
(2) go to scripts for steps 1-3.
(3) ERA5: go to data and do step4 for final input.
    GFS:  go to data and do run.sh for invariant sst/sic.
